Nokia CEO Says Already Working on Windows Phones, Reuters Says

-- B y   D i a n a   b e n - A a r o n
-- 
2011-03-18T14:36:20Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-18/nokia-ceo-says-already-working-on-windows-phones-reuters-says.html
Nokia Oyj is already working on
handsets running Microsoft Corp.’s Windows 7 operating system,
Reuters reported, citing Chief Executive Officer Stephen Elop.  “That work is already underway. If this was an acquisition
scenario, that wouldn’t be possible,” Elop said according to
